quran[431]{c,v,t}:
  67,1,TEBAREKEL-LEDHI BIJEDIHIL-MULKU WE HUWE ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN KADIRUN
  67,2,EL-LEDHI HALEKAL-MEWTE WEL-HEJÆTE LIJEBLUWEKUM ‘EJJUKUM ‘EHSENU ‘AMELÆN WE HUWEL-’AZIZUL-GAFURU
  67,3,EL-LEDHI HALEKA SEB’A SEMAWATIN TIBAKÆN MA TERA FI HALKI ER-REHMANI MIN TEFAWUTIN FARXHI’IL-BESERE HEL TERA MIN FUTURIN
  67,4,THUMME ERXHI’IL-BESERE KERRETEJNI JENKALIB ‘ILEJKEL-BESERU HASI’ÆN WE HUWE HESIRUN
  67,5,WE LEKAD ZEJJENNA ES-SEMA’E ED-DUNJA BIMESABIHE WE XHE’ALNAHA RUXHUMÆN LILSHSHEJATINI WE ‘A’TEDNA LEHUM ‘ADHABE ES-SA’IRI
  67,6,WE LILLEDHINE KEFERU BIREBBIHIM ‘ADHABU XHEHENNEME WE BI’SEL-MESIRU
  67,7,‘IDHA ‘ULKU FIHA SEMI’U LEHA SHEHIKÆN WE HIJE TEFURU
  67,8,TEKADU TEMEJJEZU MINEL-GAJDHI KULLEMA ‘ULKIJE FIHA FEWXHUN SE’ELEHUM HAZENETUHA ‘ELEM JE’TIKUM NEDHIRUN
  67,9,KALU BELA KAD XHA’ENA NEDHIRUN FEKEDHDHEBNA WE KULNA MA NEZZELEL-LAHU MIN SHEJ’IN ‘IN ‘ENTUM ‘ILLA FI DELALIN KEBIRIN
  67,10,WE KALU LEW KUNNA NESMA’U ‘EW NA’KILU MA KUNNA FI ‘ESHABI ES-SA’IRI
  67,11,FA’TEREFU BIDHENBIHIM FESUHKÆN LI’SHABI ES-SA’IRI
  67,12,‘INNEL-LEDHINE JEHSHEWNE REBBEHUM BIL-GAJBI LEHUM MEGFIRETUN WE ‘EXHRUN KEBIRUN
  67,13,WE ‘ESIRRU KAWLEKUM ‘EW EXHHERU BIHI ‘INNEHU ‘ALIMUN BIDHATI ES-SUDURI
  67,14,‘ELA JA’LEMU MEN HALEKA WE HUWEL-LETIFUL-HABIRU
  67,15,HUWEL-LEDHI XHE’ALE LEKUMUL-’ERDE DHELULÆN FAMSHU FI MENAKIBIHA WE KULU MIN RIZKIHI WE ‘ILEJHI EN-NUSHURU
  67,16,‘E’EMINTUM MEN FI ES-SEMA’I ‘EN JEHSIFE BIKUMUL-’ERDE FE’IDHA HIJE TEMURU
  67,17,‘EM ‘EMINTUM MEN FI ES-SEMA’I ‘EN JURSILE ‘ALEJKUM HASIBÆN FESETA’LEMUNE KEJFE NEDHIRI
  67,18,WE LEKAD KEDHDHEBEL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIHIM FEKEJFE KANE NEKIRI
  67,19,‘EWELEM JEREW ‘ILAT-TEJRI FEWKAHUM SAFFATIN WE JEKBIDNE MA JUMSIKUHUNNE ‘ILLA ER-REHMANU ‘INNEHU BIKULLI SHEJ’IN BESIRUN
  67,20,‘EMMEN HADHAL-LEDHI HUWE XHUNDUN LEKUM JENSURUKUM MIN DUNI ER-REHMANI ‘INIL-KAFIRUNE ‘ILLA FI GURURIN
  67,21,‘EMMEN HADHAL-LEDHI JERZUKUKUM ‘IN ‘EMSEKE RIZKAHU BEL LEXHXHU FI ‘UTUWIN WE NUFURIN
  67,22,‘EFEMEN JEMSHI MUKIBBÆN ‘ALA WEXHHIHI ‘EHDA ‘EMMEN JEMSHI SEWIJÆN ‘ALA SIRATIN MUSTEKIMIN
  67,23,KUL HUWEL-LEDHI ‘ENSHE’EKUM WE XHE’ALE LEKUMU ES-SEM’A WEL-’EBSARE WEL-’EF’IDETE KALILÆN MA TESHKURUNE
  67,24,KUL HUWEL-LEDHI DHERE’EKUM FIL-’ERDI WE ‘ILEJHI TUHSHERUNE
  67,25,WE JEKULUNE META HADHAL-WA’DU ‘IN KUNTUM SADIKINE
  67,26,KUL ‘INNEMAL-’ILMU ‘INDEL-LAHI WE ‘INNEMA ‘ENA NEDHIRUN MUBINUN
  67,27,FELEMMA RE’EWHU ZULFETEN SI’ET WUXHUHUL-LEDHINE KEFERU WE KILE HADHAL-LEDHI KUNTUM BIHI TEDDA’UNE
  67,28,KUL ‘ERE’EJTUM ‘IN ‘EHLEKENIJEL-LAHU WE MEN MA’I ‘EW REHIMENA FEMEN JUXHIRUL-KAFIRINE MIN ‘ADHABIN ‘ELIMIN
  67,29,KUL HUWE ER-REHMANU ‘AMENNA BIHI WE ‘ALEJHI TEWEKKELNA FESETA’LEMUNE MEN HUWE FI DELALIN MUBININ
  67,30,KUL ‘ERE’EJTUM ‘IN ‘ESBEHE MA’UUKUM GAWRÆN FEMEN JE’TIKUM BIMA’IN MA’ININ
  68,1,NUN WEL-KALEMI WE MA JESTURUNE
  68,2,MA ‘ENTE BINI’METI RABBIKE BIMEXHNUNIN
  68,3,WE ‘INNE LEKE LE’EXHRÆN GAJRE MEMNUNIN
  68,4,WE ‘INNEKE LE’ALA HULUKIN ‘ADHIMIN
  68,5,FESETUBSIRU WE JUBSIRUNE
  68,6,BI’EJJJIKUMUL-MEFTUNU
  68,7,‘INNE REBBEKE HUWE ‘A’LEMU BIMEN DELLE ‘AN SEBILIHI WE HUWE ‘A’LEMU BIL-MUHTEDINE
  68,8,FELA TUTI’IL-MUKEDHDHIBINE
  68,9,WE DDU LEW TUD/HINU FEJUD/HINUNE
  68,10,WE LA TUTI’ KULLE HELLAFIN MEHININ
  68,11,HEMMAZIN MESHSHA’IN BINEMIMIN
  68,12,MENNA’IN LILHAJRI MU’TEDIN ‘ETHIMIN
  68,13,‘UTULLIN BA’DE DHALIKE ZENIMIN
  68,14,‘EN KANE DHA MALIN WE BENINE
  68,15,‘IDHA TUTLA ‘ALEJHI ‘AJATUNA KALE ‘ESATIRUL-’EWWELINE
  68,16,SENESIMUHU ‘ALEL-HURTUMI
  68,17,‘INNA BELEWNAHUM KEMA BELEWNA ‘ESHABEL-XHENNETI ‘IDH ‘EKSEMU LEJESRIMUNNEHA MUSBIHINE
  68,18,WE LA JESTETHNUNE
  68,19,FETAFE ‘ALEJHA TA’IFUN MIN RABBIKE WE HUM NA’IMUNE
  68,20,FE’ESBEHET KALSSERIMI
  68,21,FETENADEW MUSBIHINE
  68,22,‘ENI EGDU ‘ALA HERTHIKUM ‘IN KUNTUM SARIMINE
  68,23,FANTELEKU WE HUM JETEHAFETUNE
  68,24,‘EN LA JEDHULENNEHAL-JEWME ‘ALEJKUM MISKINUN
  68,25,WEGADEW ‘ALA HERDIN KADIRINE
  68,26,FELEMMA RE’EWHA KALU ‘INNA LEDALLUNE
  68,27,BEL NEHNU MEHRUMUNE
  68,28,KALE ‘EWSETUHUM ‘ELEM ‘EKUL LEKUM LEWLA TUSEBBIHUNE
  68,29,KALU SUBHANE RABBINA ‘INNA KUNNA DHALIMINE
  68,30,FE’EKBELE BA’DUHUM ‘ALA BA’DIN JETELAWEMUNE
  68,31,KALU JA WEJLENA ‘INNA KUNNA TAGINE
  68,32,‘ASA REBBUNA ‘EN JUBDILENA HAJRÆN MINHA ‘INNA ‘ILA RABBINA RAGIBUNE
  68,33,KEDHALIKEL-’ADHABU WE LE’ADHABUL-’AHIRETI ‘EKBERU LEW KANU JA’LEMUNE
  68,34,‘INNE LILMUTTEKINE ‘INDE RABBIHIM XHENNATI EN-NA’IMI
  68,35,‘EFENEXH’ALUL-MUSLIMINE KALMUXHRIMINE
  68,36,MA LEKUM KEJFE TEHKUMUNE
  68,37,‘EM LEKUM KITABUN FIHI TEDRUSUNE
  68,38,‘INNE LEKUM FIHI LEMA TEHAJJERUNE
  68,39,‘EM LEKUM ‘EJMANUN ‘ALEJNA BALIGATUN ‘ILA JEWMIL-KIJAMETI ‘INNE LEKUM LEMA TEHKUMUNE
  68,40,SELHUM ‘EJJUHUM BIDHALIKE ZA’IMUN
  68,41,‘EM LEHUM SHUREKA’U FELJE’TU BISHUREKA’IHIM ‘IN KANU SADIKINE
  68,42,JEWME JUKSHEFU ‘AN SAKIN WE JUD’AWNE ‘ILA ES-SUXHUDI FELA JESTETI’UNE
  68,43,HASHI’ATEN ‘EBSARUHUM TERHEKUHUM DHILLETUN WE KAD KANU JUD’AWNE ‘ILA ES-SUXHUDI WE HUM SALIMUNE
  68,44,FEDHERNI WE MEN JUKEDHDHIBU BIHEDHAL-HEDITHI SENESTEDRIXHUHUM MIN HEJTHU LA JA’LEMUNE
  68,45,WE ‘UMLI LEHUM ‘INNE KEJDI METINUN
  68,46,‘EM TES’ELUHUM ‘EXHRÆN FEHUM MIN MEGREMIN MUTHKALUNE
  68,47,‘EM ‘INDEHUMUL-GAJBU FEHUM JEKTUBUNE
  68,48,FASBIR LIHUKMI RABBIKE WE LA TEKUN KESAHIBIL-HUTI ‘IDH NADA WE HUWE MEKDHUMUN
  68,49,LEWLA ‘EN TEDAREKEHU NI’METUN MIN RABBIHI LENUBIDHE BIL-’ARA’I WE HUWE MEDHMUMUN
  68,50,FAXHTEBAHU REBBUHU FEXHE’ALEHU MINE ES-SALIHINE
  68,51,WE ‘IN JEKADUL-LEDHINE KEFERU LEJUZLIKUNEKE BI’EBSARIHIM LEMMA SEMI’U EDH-DHIKRE WE JEKULUNE ‘INNEHU LEMEXHNUNUN
  68,52,WE MA HUWE ‘ILLA DHIKRUN LIL’ALEMINE
  69,1,EL-HAKKATU
  69,2,MAL-HAKKATU
  69,3,WE MA ‘EDRAKE MAL-HAKKATU
  69,4,KEDHDHEBET THEMUDU WE ‘ADUN BIL-KARI’ATI
  69,5,FE’EMMA THEMUDU FE’UHLIKU BIT-TAGIJETI
  69,6,WE ‘EMMA ‘ADUN FE’UHLIKU BIRIHIN SERSERIN ‘ATIJETIN
  69,7,SEHHAREHA ‘ALEJHIM SEB’A LEJALIN WE THEMANIJETE ‘EJJAMIN HUSUMÆN FETERAL-KAWME FIHA SER’A KE’ENNEHUM ‘A’XHAZU NEHLIN HAWIJETIN
  69,8,FEHEL TERA LEHUM MIN BAKIJETIN
  69,9,WE XHA’E FIR’AWNU WE MEN KABLEHU WEL-MU’UTEFIKATU BIL-HATI’ETI
  69,10,FE’ASEW RESULE RABBIHIM FE’EHADHEHUM ‘EHDHETEN RABIJETEN
  69,11,‘INNA LEMMA TEGAL-MA’U HEMELNAKUM FIL-XHARIJETI
  69,12,LINEXH’ALEHA LEKUM TEDHKIRETEN WE TA’IJEHA ‘UDHUNUN WA’IJETUN
  69,13,FE’IDHA NUFIHA FI ES-SURI NEFHATUN WAHIDETUN
  69,14,WE HUMILETIL-’ERDU WEL-XHIBALU FEDUKKETA DEKKETEN WAHIDETEN
  69,15,FEJEWME’IDHIN WEKA’ATIL-WAKI’ATU
  69,16,WE ENSHEKKATI ES-SEMA’U FEHIJE JEWME’IDHIN WE EHIJETUN
  69,17,WEL-MELEKU ‘ALA ‘ERXHA’IHA WE JEHMILU ‘ARSHE RABBIKE FEWKAHUM JEWME’IDHIN THEMANIJETUN
  69,18,JEWME’IDHIN TU’REDUNE LA TEHFA MINKUM HAFIJETUN
  69,19,FE’EMMA MEN ‘UTIJE KITABEHU BIJEMINIHI FEJEKULU HA’UUM EKRE’U KITABI
  69,20,‘INNI DHENENTU ‘ENNI MULAKIN HISABIJEH
  69,21,FEHUWE FI ‘ISHETIN RADIJETIN
  69,22,FI XHENNETIN ‘ALIJETIN
  69,23,KUTUFUHA DANIJETUN
  69,24,KULU WE ESHREBU HENI’ÆN BIMA ‘ESLEFTUM FIL-’EJJAMIL-HALIJETI
  69,25,WE ‘EMMA MEN ‘UTIJE KITABEHU BISHIMALIHI FEJEKULU JA LEJTENI LEM ‘UTE KITABIH
  69,26,WE LEM ‘EDRI MA HISABIH
  69,27,JA LEJTEHA KANETIL-KADIJETE
  69,28,MA ‘EGNA ‘ANNI MALIH
  69,29,HELEKE ‘ANNI SULTANIH
  69,30,HUDHUHU FEGULLUHU
  69,31,THUMMEL-XHEHIME SELLUHU
  69,32,THUMME FI SILSILETIN DHER’UHA SEB’UNE DHIRA’ÆN FASLUKUHU
  69,33,‘INNEHU KANE LA JU’UMINU BILLAHIL-’ADHIMI
  69,34,WE LA JEHUDDU ‘ALA TA’AMIL-MISKINI
  69,35,FELEJSE LEHUL-JEWME HAHUNA HEMIMUN
  69,36,WE LA TA’AMUN ‘ILLA MIN GISLININ
  69,37,LA JE’KULUHU ‘ILLAL-HATI’UNE
  69,38,FELA ‘UKSIMU BIMA TUBSIRUNE
  69,39,WE MA LA TUBSIRUNE
  69,40,‘INNEHU LEKAWLU RESULIN KERIMIN
  69,41,WE MA HUWE BIKAWLI SHA’IRIN KALILÆN MA TU’UMINUNE
  69,42,WE LA BIKAWLI KAHININ KALILÆN MA TEDHEKKERUNE
  69,43,TENZILUN MIN RABBIL-’ALEMINE
  69,44,WE LEW TEKAWWELE ‘ALEJNA BA’DEL-’EKAWILI
  69,45,LE’EHADHNA MINHU BIL-JEMINI
  69,46,THUMME LEKATA’NA MINHUL-WETINE
  69,47,FEMA MINKUM MIN ‘EHEDIN ‘ANHU HAXHIZINE
  69,48,WE ‘INNEHU LETEDHKIRETUN LILMUTTEKINE
  69,49,WE ‘INNA LENA’LEMU ‘ENNE MINKUM MUKEDHDHIBINE
  69,50,WE ‘INNEHU LEHESRETUN ‘ALEL-KAFIRINE
  69,51,WE ‘INNEHU LEHEKKUL-JEKINI
  69,52,FESEBBIH BIASMI RABBIKEL-’ADHIMI
  70,1,SE’ELE SA’ILUN BI’ADHABIN WAKI’IN
  70,2,LILKAFIRJNE LEJSE LEHU DAFI’UN
  70,3,MINEL-LAHI DHIL-MA’ARIXHI
  70,4,TA’RUXHUL-MELA’IKETU WE ER-RUHU ‘ILEJHI FI JEWMIN KANE MIKDARUHU HAMSINE ‘ELFE SENETIN
  70,5,FASBIR SEBRÆN XHEMILÆN
  70,6,‘INNEHUM JEREWNEHU BA’IDÆN
  70,7,WE NERAHU KARIBÆN
  70,8,JEWME TEKUNU ES-SEMA’U KALMUHLI
  70,9,WE TEKUNUL-XHIBALU KAL’IHNI
  70,10,WE LA JES’ELU HEMIMUN HEMIMÆN
  70,11,JUBESSERUNEHUM JEWEDDUL-MUXHRIMU LEW JEFTEDI MIN ‘ADHABI JEWMI’IDHIN BIBENIHI
  70,12,WE SAHIBETIHI WE ‘EHIHI
  70,13,WE FESILETIHI ELLETI TU’UWJHI
  70,14,WE MEN FIL-’ERDI XHEMI’ÆN THUMME JUNXHIHI
  70,15,KELLA ‘INNEHA LEDHA
  70,16,NEZZA’ATEN LILSHSHEWA
  70,17,TED’U MEN ‘EDBERE WE TEWELLA
  70,18,WE XHEME’A FE’EW’A
  70,19,‘INNEL-’INSANE HULIKA HELU’ÆN
  70,20,‘IDHA MESSEHU ESH-SHERRU XHEZU’ÆN
  70,21,WE ‘IDHA MESSEHUL-HAJRU MENU’ÆN
  70,22,‘ILLAL-MUSELLINE
  70,23,EL-LEDHINE HUM ‘ALA SELATIHIM DA’IMUNE
  70,24,WEL-LEDHINE FI ‘EMWALIHIM HEKKUN MA’LUMUN
  70,25,LILSSA’ILI WEL-MEHRUMI
  70,26,WEL-LEDHINE JUSEDDIKUNE BIJEWMI ED-DINI
  70,27,WEL-LEDHINE HUM MIN ‘ADHABI RABBIHIM MUSHFIKUNE
  70,28,‘INNE ‘ADHABE RABBIHIM GAJRU ME’MUNIN
  70,29,WEL-LEDHINE HUM LIFURUXHIHIM HAFIDHUNE
  70,30,‘ILLA ‘ALA ‘EZWAXHIHIM ‘EW MA MELEKET ‘EJMANUHUM FE’INNEHUM GAJRU MELUMINE
  70,31,FEMENI EBTEGA WERA’E DHALIKE FE’ULA’IKE HUMUL-’ADUNE
  70,32,WEL-LEDHINE HUM LI’MANATIHIM WE ‘AHDIHIM RA’UNE
  70,33,WEL-LEDHINE HUM BISHEHADATIHIM KA’IMUNE
  70,34,WEL-LEDHINE HUM ‘ALA SELATIHIM JUHAFIDHUNE
  70,35,‘ULA’IKE FI XHENNATIN MUKREMUNE
  70,36,FEMALIL-LEDHINE KEFERU KIBELEKE MUHTI’INE
  70,37,‘ANIL-JEMINI WE ‘ANI ESH-SHIMALI ‘IZINE
  70,38,‘EJETMA’U KULLU EMRI’IN MINHUM ‘EN JUDHALE XHENNETE NA’IMIN
  70,39,KELLA ‘INNA HALEKNAHUM MIMMA JA’LEMUNE
  70,40,FELA ‘UKSIMU BIREBBIL-MESHARIKI WEL-MEGARIBI ‘INNA LEKADIRUNE
  70,41,‘ALA ‘EN NUBEDDILE HAJRÆN MINHUM WE MA NEHNU BIMESBUKINE
  70,42,FEDHERHUM JEHUDU WE JEL’ABU HETTA JULAKU JEWMEHUMUL-LEDHI JU’ADUNE
  70,43,JEWME JEHRUXHUNE MINEL-’EXHDATHI SIRA’ÆN KE’ENNEHUM ‘ILA NUSUBIN JUFIDUNE
  70,44,HASHI’ATEN ‘EBSARUHUM TERHEKUHUM DHILLETUN DHALIKEL-JEWMUL-LEDHI KANU JU’ADUNE
  71,1,‘INNA ‘ERSELNA NUHÆN ‘ILA KAWMIHI ‘EN ‘ENDHIR KAWMEKE MIN KABLI ‘EN JE’TIJEHUM ‘ADHABUN ‘ELIMUN
  71,2,KALE JA KAWMI ‘INNI LEKUM NEDHIRUN MUBINUN
  71,3,‘ENI A’BUDU ELLAHE WE ETTEKUHU WE ‘ETI’UNI
  71,4,JEGFIR LEKUM MIN DHUNUBIKUM WE JU’UEHHIRKUM ‘ILA ‘EXHELIN MUSEMMEN ‘INNE ‘EXHELEL-LAHI ‘IDHA XHA’E LA JU’UEHHARU LEW KUNTUM TA’LEMUNE
  71,5,KALE RABBI ‘INNI DE’AWTU KAWMI LEJLÆN WE NEHARÆN
  71,6,FELEM JEZID/HUM DU’A’I ‘ILLA FIRARÆN
  71,7,WE ‘INNI KULLEMA DE’AWTUHUM LITEGFIRE LEHUM XHE’ALU ‘ESABI’AHUM FI ‘ADHANIHIM WE ESTEGSHEW THIJABEHUM WE ‘ESERRU WE ESTEKBERU ESTIKBARÆN
  71,8,THUMME ‘INNI DE’AWTUHUM XHIHARÆN
  71,9,THUMME ‘INNI ‘A’LENTU LEHUM WE ‘ESRERTU LEHUM ‘ISRARÆN
  71,10,FEKULTU ESTEGFIRU REBBEKUM ‘INNEHU KANE GAFFARÆN
  71,11,JURSILI ES-SEMA’E ‘ALEJKUM MIDRARÆN
  71,12,WE JUMDIDKUM BI’EMWALIN WE BENINE WE JEXH’AL LEKUM XHENNATIN WE JEXH’AL LEKUM ‘ENHARÆN
  71,13,MA LEKUM LA TERXHUNE LILLAHI WEKARÆN
  71,14,WE KAD HALEKAKUM ‘ETWARÆN
  71,15,‘ELEM TEREW KEJFE HALEKAL-LAHU SEB’A SEMAWATIN TIBAKÆN
  71,16,WE XHE’ALEL-KAMERE FIHINNE NURÆN WE XHE’ALE ESH-SHEMSE SIRAXHÆN
  71,17,WEL-LAHU ‘ENBETEKUM MINEL-’ERDI NEBATÆN
  71,18,THUMME JU’IDUKUM FIHA WE JUHRIXHUKUM ‘IHRAXHÆN
  71,19,WEL-LAHU XHE’ALE LEKUMUL-’ERDE BISATÆN
  71,20,LITESLUKU MINHA SUBULÆN FIXHAXHÆN
  71,21,KALE NUHUN RABBI ‘INNEHUM ‘ASEWNI WE ETTEBA’U MEN LEM JEZID/HU MALUHU WE WELEDUHU ‘ILLA HASARÆN
  71,22,WE MEKERU MEKRÆN KUBBARÆN
  71,23,WE KALU LA TEDHERUNNE ‘ALIHETEKUM WE LA TEDHERUNNE WEDDÆN WE LA SUWA’ÆN WE LA JEGUTHE WE JA’UKA WE NESRÆN
  71,24,WE KAD ‘EDELLU KETHIRÆN WE LA TEZIDI EDH-DHALIMINE ‘ILLA DELALÆN
  71,25,MIMMA HATI’ATIHIM ‘UGRIKU FE’UDHILU NARÆN FELEM JEXHIDU LEHUM MIN DUNI ELLAHI ‘ENSARÆN
  71,26,WE KALE NUHUN RABBI LA TEDHER ‘ALEL-’ERDI MINEL-KAFIRINE DEJJARÆN
  71,27,‘INNEKE ‘IN TEDHERHUM JUDILLU ‘IBADEKE WE LA JELIDU ‘ILLA FAXHIRÆN KEFFARÆN
  71,28,REBBI EGFIR LI WE LIWALIDEJJE WE LIMEN DEHALE BEJTIJE MU’UMINÆN WE LILMU’UMININE WEL-MU’UMINATI WE LA TEZIDI EDH-DHALIMINE ‘ILLA TEBARÆN
  72,1,KUL ‘UHIJE ‘ILEJJE ‘ENNEHU ESTEME’A NEFERUN MINEL-XHINNI FEKALU ‘INNA SEMI’NA KUR’ANÆN ‘AXHEBÆN
  72,2,JEHDI ‘ILA ER-RUSHDI FE’AMENNA BIHI WE LEN NUSHRIKE BIREBBINA ‘EHEDÆN
  72,3,WE ‘ENNEHU TA’ALA XHEDDU RABBINA MA ETTEHADHE SAHIBETEN WE LA WELEDÆN
  72,4,WE ‘ENNEHU KANE JEKULU SEFIHUNA ‘ALA ELLAHI SHETETÆN
  72,5,WE ‘ENNA DHENENNA ‘EN LEN TEKULEL-’INSU WEL-XHINNU ‘ALA ELLAHI KEDHIBÆN
  72,6,WE ‘ENNEHU KANE RIXHALUN MINEL-’INSI JA’UDHUNE BIRIXHALIN MINEL-XHINNI FEZADUHUM REHEKÆN
  72,7,WE ‘ENNEHUM DHENNU KEMA DHENENTUM ‘EN LEN JEB’ATHEL-LAHU ‘EHEDÆN
  72,8,WE ‘ENNA LEMESNA ES-SEMA’E FEWEXHEDNAHA MULI’ET HERESÆN SHEDIDÆN WE SHUHUBÆN
  72,9,WE ‘ENNA KUNNA NEK’UDU MINHA MEKA’IDE LILSSEM’I FEMEN JESTEMI’IL-’ANE JEXHID LEHU SHIHABÆN RESEDÆN
  72,10,WE ‘ENNA LA NEDRI ‘ESHERRUN ‘URIDE BIMEN FIL-’ERDI ‘EM ‘ERADE BIHIM REBBUHUM RESHEDÆN
  72,11,WE ‘ENNA MINNA ES-SALIHUNE WE MINNA DUNE DHALIKE KUNNA TERA’IKA KIDEDÆN
  72,12,WE ‘ENNA DHENENNA ‘EN LEN NU’XHIZEL-LAHE FIL-’ERDI WE LEN NU’XHIZEHU HEREBÆN
  72,13,WE ‘ENNA LEMMA SEMI’NAL-HUDA ‘AMENNA BIHI FEMEN JU’UMIN BIREBBIHI FELA JEHAFU BEHSÆN WE LA REHEKÆN
  72,14,WE ‘ENNA MINNAL-MUSLIMUNE WE MINNAL-KASITUNE FEMEN ‘ESLEME FE’ULA’IKE TEHERREW RESHEDÆN
  72,15,WE ‘EMMAL-KASITUNE FEKANU LIXHEHENNEME HETEBÆN
  72,16,WE ‘ELLEWI ESTEKAMU ‘ALAT-TERIKATI L’ESKAJNAHUM MA’EN GADEKÆN
  72,17,LINEFTINEHUM FIHI WE MEN JU’RID ‘AN DHIKRI RABBIHI JESLUK/HU ‘ADHABÆN SE’ADÆN
  72,18,WE ‘ENNEL-MESAXHIDE LILLAHI FELA TED’U ME’A ELLAHI ‘EHEDÆN
  72,19,WE ‘ENNEHU LEMMA KAME ‘ABDU ELLAHI JED’UHU KADU JEKUNUNE ‘ALEJHI LIBEDÆN
  72,20,KUL ‘INNEMA ‘ED’U RABBI WE LA ‘USHRIKU BIHI ‘EHEDÆN
  72,21,KUL ‘INNI LA ‘EMLIKU LEKUM DERRÆN WE LA RESHEDÆN
  72,22,KUL ‘INNI LEN JUXHIRENI MINEL-LAHI ‘EHEDUN WE LEN ‘EXHIDE MIN DUNIHI MULTEHEDÆN
  72,23,‘ILLA BELAGÆN MINEL-LAHI WE RISALATIHI WE MEN JA’SI ELLAHE WE RESULEHU FE’INNE LEHU NARE XHEHENNEME HALIDINE FIHA ‘EBEDÆN
  72,24,HETTA ‘IDHA RE’EW MA JU’ADUNE FESEJA’LEMUNE MEN ‘ED’AFU NASIRÆN WE ‘EKALLU ‘ADEDÆN
